Package com.genband.mobile.api.utilities

Class CodecSet

java.lang.Object
com.genband.mobile.api.utilities.CodecSet
public class CodecSet extends Object
CodecSet class contains all supported audio and video codec enumerators. Preferred audio codecs can be set by using instance of this object
Since:
3.0.5
